```dart
    return index == 0 && (textDirection == TextDirection.ltr || verticalDirection == VerticalDirection.down)
        || index == index.length - 1 && (textDirection == TextDirection.rtl || verticalDirection == VerticalDirection.up);
```

And also, maybe a comment for the private method like:
```dart
  // Determines if this is the first child that is being laid out 
  // by the render object, _not_ the order of the children in its list.
```

